OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police officers are being
OL,8,Finvestigated for alleged racism over
OL,9,Ftheir handling of a road crash that
OL,10,Fkilled two schoolgirls.
OL,12,FThe police watchdog said 11 officers
OL,13,Fare the subject of their probe
OL,14,Ffollowing the deaths of eight-year-
OL,15,Folds Nuria Sajjad and Selena Lau in
OL,16,Fthe incident at The Study Prep school
OL,17,Fin Wimbledon, south-west London, in
OL,18,FJuly 2023.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe families of the two girls have
OL,8,Fsaid the "truth must come to light"
OL,9,Fafter the Independent Office for
OL,10,FPolice Conduct's (IOPC) investigation
OL,11,Fwas announced, adding: "We were
OL,12,Funconvinced that the investigation was
OL,13,Fconducted thoroughly."
OL,15,FIn June 2024, the Metropolitan Police
OL,16,Fsaid the driver of the 44 which
OL,17,Fcrashed into the school, Claire
OL,18,FFreemantle, had suffered an epileptic
OL,19,Fseizure and would face no criminal
OL,20,Fcharges.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@cO]sD@XOUuD@VO]xD@YOZ
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FShe was rearrested and released on
OL,8,Fbail pending further investigation in
OL,9,FJanuary last year.
OL,11,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,12,Fsaid there are "some further factors
OL,13,Fwe must consider" before making a
OL,14,Fcharging decision.
OL,16,FIn a statement issued on Tuesday, the
OL,17,FIOPC said it was probing allegations
OL,18,Fthat officers provided "false and
OL,19,Fmisleading information" to the
OL,20,Ffamilies following complaints about
OL,21,Fthe standard of the investigation.
OL,26,@tD@POUuD@QO]zD@XOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe watchdog said the complaints
OL,8,Frelated to the force's "management and
OL,9,Fdirection, the conduct of the
OL,10,Finvestigation team, and their
OL,11,Fengagement with the victims".
OL,13,FFour serving officers, including a
OL,14,Fcommander and a detective chief
OL,15,Finspector, are being investigated for
OL,16,Fgross misconduct, the IOPC said.
OL,26,@pD@XOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FReacting to the latest update, the
OL,8,Fgirls' families said in a statement:
OL,9,F"On the 6th of July 2023, our lives
OL,10,Fwere irreparably shattered by a cruel
OL,11,Ftragedy.
OL,13,F"The past 33 months have been
OL,14,Fincredibly difficult for everyone
OL,15,Faffected including those who lost
OL,16,Ffamily, were seriously injured or
OL,17,Fwitnessed the horrific incident, and
OL,18,Fwe are still trying to come to terms
OL,19,Fwith what happened on that fateful day.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We have always maintained that the
OL,8,Finitial investigation was flawed.
OL,10,F"When the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,11,Ftook the decision for no further
OL,12,Faction against the driver on the 26th
OL,13,Fof June 2024, we asserted that the
OL,14,Foriginal investigation was poor, and
OL,15,Fwe were unconvinced that the
OL,16,Finvestigation was conducted thoroughly.
OL,18,F"We are encouraged that the
OL,19,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct
OL,20,Fhave opened an inquiry.
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We have always sought the truth, and
OL,8,Fwill continue to champion the pursuit
OL,9,Fof complete clarity on the events of
OL,10,Fthat devastating day and subsequent
OL,11,Factions taken by the Metropolitan
OL,12,FPolice.
OL,14,F"The truth must come to light."
OL,16,FProsecutors wrote to the victims'
OL,17,Ffamilies on Friday to say they
OL,18,Fexpected to be able to announce
OL,19,Fwhether or not they had reached a
OL,20,Fcharging decision by the end of April.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe families are due to meet with the
OL,8,FCPS on later today for an update.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the CPS said:
OL,11,F"After careful consideration of all
OL,12,Fthe evidence and material provided by
OL,13,Fthe police as part of this
OL,14,Freinvestigation, and upon receipt of
OL,15,Fadvice from counsel on 7 April, we
OL,16,Fhave concluded that there are some
OL,17,Ffurther factors we must consider
OL,18,Fbefore a decision on charge can be
OL,19,Freached.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We appreciate the ongoing distress
OL,8,Fany delay may cause and are committed
OL,9,Fto making a final decision as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible."
OL,12,FConfirming the watchdog's
OL,13,Finvestigation, IOPC director Amanda
OL,14,FRowe said: "The complaints relate to
OL,15,Fconcerns about the standard of the
OL,16,Finvestigation, including its
OL,17,Fmanagement and direction, the conduct
OL,18,Fof the investigation team, and their
OL,19,Fengagement with the victims.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]vD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We are also investigating allegations
OL,8,Fthat Met officers provided false and
OL,9,Fmisleading information to those
OL,10,Faffected and whether the officers'
OL,11,Ftreatment of those affected was
OL,12,Finfluenced by their race.
OL,14,F"We have now served notices advising
OL,15,Ffour serving officers, whose ranks are
OL,16,Fcommander, detective chief inspector,
OL,17,Fdetective sergeant and detective
OL,18,Fconstable, and a former detective
OL,19,Finspector, that their conduct is being
OL,20,Finvestigated at the level of gross
OL,21,Fmisconduct.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Two detective constables are being
OL,8,Finvestigated at misconduct level.
OL,10,F"Our investigation is ongoing and
OL,11,Fshould any further conduct issues be
OL,12,Fidentified then officers will be
OL,13,Fserved notices.
OL,15,F"All officers served notices will be
OL,16,Finterviewed in due course. The serving
OL,17,Fof notices does not mean that
OL,18,Fproceedings will necessarily follow.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMs Rowe said IOPC investigators have
OL,8,Fmet with the families and the officers
OL,9,Fleading the Met Police's new
OL,10,Finvestigation into the tragedy.
OL,12,FThe director said: "At the end of our
OL,13,Finvestigation, we will decide whether
OL,14,Fany officers have a disciplinary case
OL,15,Fto answer in respect of the conduct
OL,16,Fallegations."
OL,18,FThe Met submitted a full file of
OL,19,Fevidence to the CPS on March 17 after
OL,20,Fit reopened the investigation on
OL,21,FOctober 24, 2024.
OL,26,@tD@TOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FCommander Charmain Brenyah, from the
OL,8,FMet's Roads and Transport Policing
OL,9,FCommand, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,10,Fwith Nuria and Selena's families, as
OL,11,Fwell as everyone who has been impacted
OL,12,Fby this terrible tragedy.
OL,14,F"We understand this prolonged process
OL,15,Fhas compounded their grief and
OL,16,Fsuffering.
OL,26,@qD@POUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776345056
OL,3,CMet officers probed over alleged
OL,4,Cracism in handling of Wimbledon school
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"It is right that our initial handling
OL,8,Fof this incident be independently
OL,9,Fscrutinised, and we will provide every
OL,10,Fassistance to the IOPC as their
OL,11,Finvestigation continues."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/14
